author: @SeemeSeeyou
text: Holy Spirit come into my life and be my advocate for the things that are going on in my life. Give me the wisdom to discern between what battles to fight and not fight. Help me to let go and let God. In Jesus Name.  Amen

author: @SeemeSeeyou
text: God said: "If you never felt pain, how would you know I am a healer. If you never felt sadness, how would you know I am a comforter?"

author: @SeemeSeeyou
text: Lord every breath we have is a gift from You  I pray for my Husband right now in the Name of Jesus the Name that is above all other names & I ask for complete release from whatever is causing these pains/difficulties I believe You are our healer today 🙏🙏🎚

author: @SeemeSeeyou
text: Thank you Lord for the bills being paid, Food on the table, clothes on our back, roof over our head, my family and friends in great health. Please stop the violence and shooting in my city. Children are being hurt. Please protect them from all hurt, harm, and danger.

author: @SeemeSeeyou
text: Please Pray for me. I need JESUS to take the pain away.

author: @SeemeSeeyou
text: I command every fiery diet to misfire concerning my Husband and I, my family, my friends, and even the foe. No weapon formed shall prosper.
